1
00:00:10,550 --> 00:00:14,520
I've had many one-sided loves
 since childhood.

2
00:00:14,600 --> 00:00:17,560
- Uncomfortable?
- No, I'm good.

3
00:00:22,640 --> 00:00:25,690
Akari, Age 21

4
00:00:26,990 --> 00:00:29,610
Okay, good.

5
00:00:27,980 --> 00:00:29,780
Yukako, Age 21.

6
00:00:44,380 --> 00:00:46,170
You know, Akari.

7
00:00:47,050 --> 00:00:48,260
Hm?

8
00:00:51,640 --> 00:00:52,970
You're cute.

9
00:01:00,810 --> 00:01:02,900
I felt like crying.

10
00:01:30,300 --> 00:01:33,390
I might be embarrassing myself here, but...

11
00:01:34,470 --> 00:01:38,270
are you interested in anyone now?

12
00:01:46,190 --> 00:01:48,190
If you want to invite anyone to the BBQ,

13
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:50,610
we welcome surprise guests!

14
00:02:03,540 --> 00:02:05,910
Ayano

